Mg Car Survival V4
==================


MAP INFO
==================

*There are 4 maps to play on, one of the maps will be chosen automatically after 5 seconds from spawn.

*You need to survive 100 seconds through each map by dodging the cars, if you survive all the way through, you will be challenged to a knife fight with the other team.

*The map is based on random cases and sometimes there can be a lot of cars, but sometimes there's not as many.

*This map will require the noblock plugin to work properly.

*There are 64 player slots so it can easily go on any server.


NOTES
==================
*It's the final version of mg car survival maps...I'm out of ideas for this kind of maps....

*Some people find this map annoying but some people find this map fun, so it's your choice.


Enjoy
------------------
